From e3cf889d81d30da2a697a98a4014ba5bb772bc38 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Eric Yang <eric.yang.wiwynn@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 21 Apr 2026 11:21:23 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] platform-mc: Defer FRU decorators until data

Move the Decorator interfaces (Asset, AssetTag, Revision, Compatible)
out of PldmEntityReq into a new PldmFruDecorators class. PldmEntityReq
now only inherits the entity-type-specific Inventory.Item interface,
keeping the D-Bus object lightweight at creation time.

PldmFruDecorators is created lazily via ensureFruDecorators(), a helper
called only inside the switch cases that actually set a Decorator
property. Field types that do not map to a Decorator property (IANA,
Vendor, Chassis, etc.) never trigger creation, even though the PLDM FRU
spec permits a terminus to provide only those fields.

Motivation:
Termini that do not support PLDM FRU commands never receive FRU record
data, so updateInventoryWithFru() is never called for them. Previously
the decorator interfaces were registered unconditionally, exposing empty
properties on D-Bus for these termini. Empty interfaces pollute
inventory tool output and may mislead D-Bus consumers that check
interface presence to determine whether FRU data is available.

Tested:
On Yosemite 4 platform with mixed terminus types.

Terminus without PLDM FRU support (OpenBIC, SENTINEL_DOME_SLOT_1):

    $ busctl introspect xyz.openbmc_project.PLDM \
        .../inventory/system/board/SENTINEL_DOME_SLOT_1
    xyz...Inventory.Item.Board  interface

Only Inventory.Item.Board present, no Decorator interfaces.

Terminus with FRU data (Mellanox NIC, Terminus_1):

    $ busctl introspect xyz.openbmc_project.PLDM \
        .../inventory/system/board/Terminus_1
    xyz...Inventory.Decorator.Asset      interface
      .Manufacturer   "MLNX"
      .Model          "CX71343DM"
      .PartNumber     "CX71343DMC-VEAF_FB"
      .SerialNumber   "MT2408J008NE"
    xyz...Inventory.Decorator.AssetTag   interface
    xyz...Inventory.Decorator.Compatible interface
      .Names          "ConnectX-7 ..."
    xyz...Inventory.Decorator.Revision   interface
      .Version        "28.41.1000"
    xyz...Inventory.Item.Board           interface

All four Decorator interfaces appear with populated values only
when the terminus provides FRU record data.

Change-Id: I754286b23325506d3a15b409e5b48bd04682275f
Signed-off-by: Eric Yang <eric.yang.wiwynn@gmail.com>
